Spree Payment Surcharges
=====================

Allows you to add a surcharge to your payments to help recoup costs.

Install
=======

Add this line to your gem file:

    gem 'spree_payment_surcharges', :git => 'git://github.com/complistic-gaff/spree-payment-surcharges.git'
    
Go to the payments admin and enjoy :)

